<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?><Regulation lims:pit-date="2008-02-28" lims:lastAmendedDate="2008-02-28" lims:current-date="2019-06-21" lims:inforce-start-date="2008-02-28" lims:fid="602641" lims:id="602641" gazette-part="II" regulation-type="SI" xml:lang="fr" xmlns:lims="http://justice.gc.ca/lims"><Identification lims:inforce-start-date="2008-02-28" lims:fid="602642" lims:id="602642"><InstrumentNumber>TR/2008-28</InstrumentNumber><RegistrationDate><Date><YYYY>2008</YYYY><MM>3</MM><DD>19</DD></Date></RegistrationDate><ConsolidationDate lims:inforce-start-date="2008-02-28"><Date><YYYY>2019</YYYY><MM>6</MM><DD>22</DD></Date></ConsolidationDate><EnablingAuthority lims:inforce-start-date="2008-02-28" lims:fid="602644" lims:id="602644"><XRefExternal reference-type="act" link="F-11">LOI SUR LA GESTION DES FINANCES PUBLIQUES</XRefExternal></EnablingAuthority><LongTitle lims:inforce-start-date="2008-02-28" lims:fid="602645" lims:id="602645">Décret de remise visant la vente du Fisherman’s Wharf de Digby</LongTitle><RegulationMakerOrder><RegulationMaker>C.P.</RegulationMaker><OrderNumber>2008-405</OrderNumber><Date><YYYY>2008</YYYY><MM>2</MM><DD>28</DD></Date></RegulationMakerOrder></Identification><Order lims:inforce-start-date="2008-02-28" lims:fid="602646" lims:id="602646"><Provision lims:inforce-start-date="2008-02-28" lims:fid="602647" lims:id="602647" format-ref="indent-0-0" language-align="yes"><Text>Sur recommandation du ministre des Transports, de l’Infrastructure et des Collectivités et du Conseil du Trésor et en vertu du paragraphe 23(2.1)<FootnoteRef idref="nbp_1012f_tc_2281">a</FootnoteRef> de la <XRefExternal reference-type="act" link="F-11">Loi sur la gestion des finances publiques</XRefExternal><FootnoteRef idref="nbp_1012f_tc_2282">b</FootnoteRef>, Son Excellence la Gouverneure générale en conseil, estimant que l’intérêt public le justifie, prend le <XRefExternal reference-type="regulation" link="TR-2008-28">Décret de remise visant la vente du Fisherman’s Wharf de Digby</XRefExternal>, ci-après.</Text><Footnote id="nbp_1012f_tc_2281" placement="page" status="official"><Label>a</Label><Text>L.C. 1991, ch. 24, par. 7(2)</Text></Footnote><Footnote id="nbp_1012f_tc_2282" placement="page" status="official"><Label>b</Label><Text>L.R., ch. F-11</Text></Footnote></Provision></Order><Body lims:inforce-start-date="2008-02-28" lims:fid="602648" lims:id="602648"><Heading lims:inforce-start-date="2008-02-28" lims:fid="602649" lims:id="602649" level="1"><TitleText>Remise</TitleText></Heading><Section lims:inforce-start-date="2008-02-28" lims:lastAmendedDate="2008-02-28" lims:fid="602650" lims:id="602650"><Label>1</Label><Text>Est accordée à la <Language xml:lang="en">Maritime Harbours Society</Language> la remise d’une dette de 480 500 $ due à Sa Majesté en vertu d’un accord signé le 21 octobre 1999 conformément au Programme de cession des ports.</Text></Section><Heading lims:inforce-start-date="2008-02-28" lims:fid="602651" lims:id="602651" level="1"><TitleText>Condition</TitleText></Heading><Section lims:inforce-start-date="2008-02-28" lims:lastAmendedDate="2008-02-28" lims:fid="602652" lims:id="602652"><Label>2</Label><Text>La remise est accordée à la condition que la <Language xml:lang="en">Maritime Harbours Society</Language> fournisse à Sa Majesté, représentée par le ministre des Transports, la preuve de la vente du <Language xml:lang="en">Fisherman’s Wharf</Language> de Digby à la <Language xml:lang="en">Digby Harbour Port Association</Language>.</Text></Section></Body></Regulation>